data.name: Beatraptor
data.desc: Negate the effects of monsters in the Extra Monster Zones while this card is in the Main Monster Zone. When this card is destroyed by battle: You can Special Summon 1 "Beatraptor" from your Deck. You can only use this effect of "Beatraptor" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
